name: wincache_rplist_fileinfo
purpose: Retrieves information about resolve file path cache

return.description:
Array of meta data about the resolve file path cache  or FALSE on failureThe array returned by this function contains the following elements:
   
    
     
      total_file_count - total number of file path 
       mappings stored in the cache
     
    
    
     
      rplist_entries - an array that contains the information about all 
       the cached file paths:
      
       
        
         resolve_path - path to a file
        
       
       
        
         subkey_data - corresponding absolute path to a file
